de, R., Bull, J.J., (1989) Ecology, 70, p. 1657; Case, T.J., Taper, M.L., (2000) Am. Nat., 155, p. 583; Smith, F.A., Betancourt, J.L., Brown, J.H., (1995) Science, 270, p. 2012; Hadly, E.A., Kohn, M.H., Leonard, J.A., Wayne, R.K., (1998) Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. U.S.A., 95, p. 6893; Chiba, S., (1998) Paleobiology, 24, p. 99; Haffer, J., (1969) Science, 165, p. 131; Losos, J.B., Warhelt, K.I., Schoener, T.W., (1997) Nature, 386, p. 70; Huey, R.B., Gilchrist, G.W., Carlson, M.L., Berrigan, D., Serra, L., (2000) Science, 287, p. 308; Bell, M.A., Andrews, C.A., (1997) Evolutionary Ecology of Freshwater Animals, pp. 323-363. , B. Streit, T. Städler, C. M. Lively, Eds. (Birkhäuser Verlag, Basel, Switzerland); Rundle, H.D., Nagel, L., Boughman, J.W., Schluter, D., (2000) Science, 287, p. 306; Folmer, O., Black, M., Hoeh, W., Lutz, R., Vrijenhoek, R., (1994) Mol. Mar. Biol. Biotechnol., 3, p. 294; Swofford, D.L., (1998) PAUP*: Phylogenetic Analysis Using Parsimony (and Other Methods), version 4.062a, , Sinauer, Sunderland, MA; Schneider, S., Roessli, D., Excoffier, L., (2000) Arlequin: A Software for Population Genetics Data Analysis, version 2.000, , Genetics and Biometry Lab, Department of Anthropology, Univ. of Geneva, Switzerland; Roy, K., Foote, M., (1997) Trends Ecol. Evol., 12, p. 277; Nei, M., (1987) Molecular Evolutionary Genetics, , Columbia Univ. Press, New York; Tajima, F., (1983) Genetics, 105, p. 437; note","Roy, K.; Section of Ecology, Division of Biology, University of California, 9500 Gilman Drive, San Diego, CA 92093-0116, United States; email: kroy@biomail.ucsd.edu",,,,,,,,00368075,,SCIEA,11387473,"English","Science",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-0035368547
